ust upload, convert, and download.","faq_title":"FAQ","faq_1_q":"Can I merge multiple images into one PDF?","faq_1_a":"Yes. Select multiple images and we will combine them into a single PDF in your chosen order.","faq_2_q":"Will the image quality be reduced?","faq_2_a":"No. We keep your image quality as much as possible when wrapping them into a PDF.","faq_3_q":"Can I convert ID photos to PDF?","faq_3_a":"Yes. It is great for ID documents and form submissions that require PDF format.","faq_4_q":"Will the output file be huge?","faq_4_a":"We apply reasonable compression while keeping quality, so the PDF remains easy to share and upload.","merge_failed_alert":"Something went wrong during merging. Please try again.","download_file_prefix":"ImageToPDF"},"footer":{"more_links":{"image_to_pdf":"Imagem para PDF","pdf_to_images":"PDF para imagens","image_remove_text":"Remover texto da imagem","image_replace_text":"Substituir texto na imagem","poster_change_text":"Editar texto do p\xf4ster","ecommerce_main_image_change_text":"Editar texto da imagem principal de e‑commerce","wechat_alipay_screenshot_change_text":"Editar texto da captura WhatsApp/PayPal","payment_screenshot_change_text":"Editar texto da captura de pagamento","watermark_camera_change_text":"Editar texto da marca d’\xe1gua","exam_score_screenshot_change_text":"Editar texto da captura de notas","leave_note_image_change_text":"Editar texto da imagem de licen\xe7a","certificate_image_change_text":"Editar texto da imagem de certificado","call_sms_image_change_text":"Editar texto da captura de chamadas/SMS","ticket_image_change_text":"Editar texto da captura de bilhete","fix_text_in_image":"Corrigir texto na imagem"}},"common":{"yes":"Sim","no":"N\xe3o","more":"Mais","collapse":"Recolher"},"call_sms_image_change_text":{"meta":{"title":"Editar texto em captura de chamadas/SMS - PhoText","keywords":"editar texto chamadas sms, editar captura de chamadas, editar captura sms, editar texto em captura","description":"Edite t